---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
---

<Layout title="About" description={`About ${config.author.name}`}>
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    
    <p class="lead">
      I'm <strong>Jonathan D. Rhyne</strong>—a lawyer by training, an engineer at heart, and these days the co-founder & CEO of <a href="https://nutrient.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Nutrient.io</a>.
    </p>

    <p>
      We build developer-first tools that let teams create, collaborate on, and automate documents across every major framework and device. After growing PSPDFKit from a weekend project into the industry-standard PDF SDK, I led our rebrand to Nutrient to reflect a bigger mission: helping the world innovate beyond paper.
    </p>

    <h2>What I'm building</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Nutrient Web Viewer & APIs</strong> — headless, high-fidelity document tooling for modern web apps</li>
      <li><strong>Low-code workflow automation</strong> — bringing citizen developers the same superpowers power users enjoy</li>
      <li><strong>AI document assistants</strong> — marrying LLMs with rock-solid SDKs so devs can ship magical experiences in hours, not months</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Principles I live by</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Extreme ownership</strong> — low ego, high accountability</li>
      <li><strong>Relentless curiosity</strong> — ship fast, learn faster</li>
      <li><strong>Single-threaded focus</strong> — one priority at a time for compounding results</li>
      <li><strong>Bias for action</strong> — momentum beats perfection</li>
      <li><strong>Radical candor</strong> — honest, respectful feedback fuels growth</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Beyond work</h2>
    <p>When I'm not obsessing over developer experience, you'll find me:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>On the pitch — fundraising my cardio keeping up with rec-league soccer</li>
      <li>Under dark skies — astrophotography and teaching my kids the constellations</li>
      <li>At the North Carolina coast — chasing sunrises, not deadlines</li>
      <li>Behind a Leica — minimalist, black-and-white street shots</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <p>
      Building something that needs best-in-class document workflows? 
      <a href={`mailto:${config.social.email}`}>Ping me</a>—always up for chatting code, coffee, or clever growth loops.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about ul, .about ol {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .about li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .about hr {
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }
</style>
